---
description: Testing, evidence and release-quality rules
globs: ["**/*.test.*", "**/*.spec.*", "tests/**", ".github/workflows/**"]
alwaysApply: false
---

- Test behavior, authorization, audit and persistence—not only UI rendering.
- Use synthetic data.
- Do not delete or weaken tests merely to pass.
- Every phase needs automated evidence and a simple manual checklist when user-facing.
- No milestone passes with unresolved Severity 1 or 2 defects.
- Financial reconciliation variance must be INR 0.00.
